name: The first step to the new world

metadata.name: Gate of Heaven
metadata.description:
"Gate of Heaven" is intended to show the knowledge we need to be able to change our lives. Many people understand very late that we are raised and taught to be employees. The media has a great influence on our daily thought processes and often influences us negatively. We are constantly confronted with fear and panic. This ensures that we are also afraid to develop and become independent.

Therefore, it is important not to confront our subconscious with negative news or negative people. Our creativity suffers greatly from this.

We have the ability to program our subconscious. Everything we can imagine, we can manifest and thus realize. You can do anything! You just have to ask yourself the right question. Namely: "What makes you happy?" When you have the answer, nothing stands in your way! 

The first step to the new world! 

Reset you mind and program your subconscious! This is the first step to success!

Enter your own Gate of Heaven and create the world behind it!

5500x8000px
